  "title": "chore(examples): add e-commerce widgets [part 1]",
  "body": "_This is part 1 of the series \"e-commerce demo\"._\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nThis PR scaffolds the e-commerce demo with InstantSearch.js widgets. It was generated using [Create InstantSearch App](https://github.com/algolia/create-instantsearch-app).\r\n\r\n## Notes\r\n\r\n- Everything in the demo was achieved without connectors\r\n- `algoliasearch` and `instantsearch.js` deps are added as dependencies to trigger less network requests (not loading from a CDN) and to leverage Renovate\r\n- The ES build of `instantsearch.js` is used\r\n- It doesn't include voice search because the designs are not done yet\r\n\r\n## Preview\r\n\r\nThere's currently no styles in this part 1.\r\n\r\n[See preview →](https://deploy-preview-3799--instantsearchjs.netlify.com/examples/e-commerce/)\r\n\r\n## Related\r\n\r\n- [E-commerce demo design](https://app.zeplin.io/project/5acc8becfc0c980068fc12cc/screen/5cd1a7992e4f02039b5a8336)\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nThe styles will come in a stacked PR.",
